Interface JCL_message_register

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Constant, JCL_message, java.io.Serializable

    public interface JCL_message_register
extends JCL_message, Constant
    Version:
    1.0 enables JCL register a JAVA component (jars). After a registration an execution is possible in JCL.
    Author:
    Joubert
